menuconfig ZLIBS_UTILS_SETTINGS
    bool "Settings"
    default n
    select FLASH
    select FLASH_MAP
    select SETTINGS
    select ZMS
    help
      Enable the zlibs wrapper around the Zephyr settings subsystem.

      The library loads a typed settings subtree and persists updates through
      Zephyr settings backends. The Kconfig integration in this module assumes
      the ZMS-backed settings storage.
